FBIS4-5164 "dreas068_c_94013" FBIS-EAS-94-068 Daily Report 8 Apr 1994 North Korea Agreements Signed on Information Services Agreements Signed on Information Services With Cambodia SK0804053294 Pyongyang KCNA in English 0459 GMT 8 Apr 94 SK0804053294 Pyongyang KCNA English BFN [Text] Pyongyang, April 8 (KCNA) -- An agreement on cooperation in information services between the Information Committee of the DPRK and the Ministry of Information of the Government of the Kingdom of Cambodia was signed in Phnom Penh on April 4. It was signed by vice-chairman of the DPRK Information Committee Yi Pong-hui and Minister of Information of Cambodia Ieng Mouly.
